HEADWORD: Mulloid
<hw>Mul"loid</hw> <pr>(m⟦ucr⟧l"loid)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[NL.
<ets>Mullus</ets>, generic name (fr. L. <ets>mullus</ets> surmullet) +
<ets>-oid</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Like or pertaining to
the genus <gen>Mullus</gen>, which includes the surmullet, or red
mullet.</def>⟦br⟧
